cff-version: 1.2.0
title: LLM Guard Bench — Automated Adversarial Attack Benchmark Suite
abstract: |
  A research-grade, production-ready framework for systematically evaluating the
  robustness of Large Language Models against adversarial attack vectors through
  multi-stage concurrent attacks, dual-ledger auditing, and automated vulnerability
  analytics with enterprise-grade error handling and resource management.

